{"tid":1970628,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港澳辦：強烈譴責反對派拖延內會主席選舉","createTime":"2020-04-13T09:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T10:54:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"42dc5fedd03790044a1766a83ada7af6387a255c","tid":1970628,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:37:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港澳辦強烈譴責反對派議員拖延內會主席選舉，指行為構成公職人員行為失當。<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦回應香港立法會至今仍未選出內務委員會主席，發言人不點名指，主持內會主席選舉的議員以及部分反對派議員濫用權力，借程序問題惡意拖延，致使內會六個月仍無法選出主席，已經嚴重影響立法會正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n在當前嚴峻疫情下，議員應急市民所急，以大局為重，履行應盡職責，但一些反對派議員為謀取政治私利，罔顧公眾利益，癱瘓立法會運作，行為屬政治攬炒，其所作所為令人質疑，有違宣誓誓言，構成公職人員行為失當，對此予以強烈譴責。"},{"pid":"cafa7095712df6dc4073ba7b039d24d686bc136a","tid":1970628,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=387583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387583&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWeojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=cd23e8be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387583&h=1d6ab8bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=387583</a>"},{"pid":"2ee1b8394beb670ce4eabd8e02bf6d095e48fcdf","tid":1970628,"uid":205462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:55:28.000Z","msg":"基本法第22條幾時立法?"},{"pid":"1ab2ae3907fb5a90e5606d77fb5085760157f731","tid":1970628,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"企撚開d啦"},{"pid":"82c0bbeef2d3568d877958f1e1726d85b2bb5ed7","tid":1970628,"uid":59922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:57:09.000Z","msg":"凡是敵人反對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">基本法第22條幾時立法?</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d7c824c1f2be7819c6e371c07975649